# Basic Inventory Management

A simple inventory management system built using VB.NET. This project allows users to manage product information, including categories, descriptions, quantities, and prices. It is suitable for small-scale businesses or personal use to track inventory effectively.
## Features

- Add, update, and delete products.
- Organize products into categories (e.g., Drinks, Household, Snacks, etc.).
- Display all inventory in a DataGridView.
- Calculate total inventory value based on quantity and price.
## Technologies Used

- Programming Language: VB.NET
- Framework: Windows Forms Application
- IDE: Visual Studio
